column5: Just took them off the Weber Smokey Mountain Cooker, attempting to wait for the baked potatoes to finish.... don't know if I can.....    Burt
They look real good Burt!!!   ... all you need to go with them is some cornbread and Collard Greens!!!
That looks appetizing Burtess    What time you said we should get to your place
Cooked to perfection, would go great with my char broiled rib eye. What sauce are you using Burtess?
Yeah, they were pretty good.  Used a mix of Bull's-Eye Original and Chicken & Rib, with some rub mixed in....  Burt
If Walleye had ribs like that I'd fish Erie more often! Those look gooooood! Can I be your friend?
mmmmmm your killin me here!   Hawk
